---
title: SuperQuick Zesty Sausage and Tortellini Soup with Fresh Veggies
description: Chockfull of veggie goodness and cozy flavours — not to mention pillowy tortellini — this lightning-fast sausage soup supper delivers on maximum flavour in minimal time.

